Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:46.49,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}嘘の付けない君が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:48.88,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}夢が破れて
