Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:14.49,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,好害羞  玩偶裝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說綾音那裡也被偷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是放在櫥櫃裡的飯團
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小偷跑進神社裡會遭天遣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,島上會出現小偷  真少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近谷類和蔬菜  好像都被偷了好幾棵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有點不安心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  究竟是誰做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人  今天還真早…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的臉上有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,便當…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這是熊熊的蜜罐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人是姐姐大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我吃的  承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就承認了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  雖然飯團  水果  蜂蜜  饅頭是我吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:03:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他可不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道認為偷全村食物的小偷會是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人的平時的行為太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連行人大人都這樣看待我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會失落成這樣  就是說真的不是麻知姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行蹤不明的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快  行人大人一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在違抗姐姐大人的話會很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也不能放任小偷不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢  我們也幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那分頭找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在三天前被偷的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那被偷什麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害  沒看到過這麼拼命的麻知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼麻煩的事情誰去做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會去的…樂意至極…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來被偷的很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事件從村子最北邊開始慢慢延伸到南邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後昨晚是海龍神社
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說  小偷盯上的下個地方會是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,離這條線最近的家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那大概會是香里家或者是雪乃家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:05:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  那麼今晚只要去監視的話也許就能抓住犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼為分兩組的抽籤  不准互相抱怨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會又使詐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你先抽不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了你乾杯  發光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和公子一起在夕陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情…那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直玩到天亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,勝小鈴的機會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我先來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們去香里家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:07:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之晚上不得不聚在一起守小偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小偷會是怎麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這島上以前都沒有過這種壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行…行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是小偷做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把這些全部都吃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明每天都只偷一家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天卻是海龍神社和黃瓜地兩家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和以往推想的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小偷會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很想睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人還沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在家的時候常常開夜車的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐氣勢十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為被誣陷了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別睜著眼睡覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣…就不會困了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此…彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  貓頭鷹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然接住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這麼黑的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會讓你逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就揭穿你的真實面目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我老實點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,頭部脫出了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被砍下的人頭?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,頭…被拽下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是個頭套
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  為什麼是這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看守的話我一個人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:10:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很累
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先睡吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,浴室裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人來  小鈴就待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了  小偷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你認識的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次見到的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…冷靜點…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,簍筐?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像冷靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  為什麼要鑽進簍筐裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不擅長在別人面前露面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一家都在演雜技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  我從以前開始就很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在舞台上一直失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了克服害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了獨自的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我還是和以前一樣無法和人交談
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,避人眼目在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能好好地交到朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是這樣的我在途中也交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人開始一起旅行不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,錢用光了想坐船回國的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被暴風雨捲入…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,醒來的時候就發現漂流到這個島上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 也不用一一畫在紙上說明…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然每天都下決心…今天要出現在大家面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又太害羞又猶豫起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  這樣就事件解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過偷東西可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…想讓你們分我點東西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻開不了口…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心就…對不起了…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  黃瓜地的是不是太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  把田地全都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…不知道…那不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那究竟是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是遠野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的人果然很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是說我也很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黃瓜地也許是你的朋友做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野先生非常喜歡黃瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那朋友也漂流到了這個島上太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知被嫁禍了不是很生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是知道梅梅是犯人  不知道會做出什麼事情來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先回家  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  麻知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音把這個給我 說是犯人似乎戴著這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紙糊的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅連這個都戴著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太害羞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在追蹤這個氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到也是時間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:15:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這回是千影家的黃瓜地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都到這個程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道黃瓜小偷是誰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這氣味和剛才面具的是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧  氣味消失了 難道是錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在這種地方徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說了嗎  被抓住就很糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了  在我回這裡之前要老實待著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野先生…遠野先生是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…都兩人一起旅行著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想到遠野先生就在附近  就坐立不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想快點見到朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…行人先生  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  犬犬好像知道遠野先生在哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,氣味消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要跳過去的話有點遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也沒有可以藏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無法騙過我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐…聽我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道你是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:07.26,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我找的多幸苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:08.85,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.77,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,都叫你不要亂跑亂動了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.86,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:17.19,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是河童嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫遠野先生一直以為是人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河童什麼虛構動物根本不可能存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是烏龜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事情無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然嫁禍給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然向我挑釁  真有勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…請等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偷食物的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野先生沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是真正的犯人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢陷害我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起…饒恕我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對做壞事的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要給予懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她也好好道歉了 就饒恕她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了  麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道理由  看起來不像是壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被人誤會是大姐頭平時的行為不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經那麼道歉了  還懲罰的話那是魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺我才是壞人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然行人大人這樣說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝…謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咬了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烏龜…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難得平復下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  你是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.07,0:23:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此島上增加了新的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:03.68,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.68,0:23:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,梅梅和遠野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是非常奇怪的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這島上的卻人也非常的和藹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許很快就會令人意外地融洽相處了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人…活該…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心情不好
